 alt=\"\" width=\"175\" height=\"200\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Brent from <a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SnowVPS</a> has recently sent in their first offer ever to LowEndBox! They are offering OpenVZ and KVM based virtual services out of Chicago, IL. We hope you enjoy what they have to offer and we look forward to hearing any of your questions/comments/feedback below!</p><p>Their WHOIS is public and you can find their <a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/legal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ToS/Legal Docs here.</a> They accept Credit Cards, PayPal, and Bitcoins/Altcoins as payment methods.</p><p><strong>Here\u2019s what they had to say:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cSnowVPS is a web server provider with servers based out of Chicago, Illinois. We provide both KVM and OpenVZ virtualized servers, and all of our plans use SSD drives to offer blazing high performance. What sets us apart is the personalized and human experience you get when you are a SnowVPS customer. From day one, one on one support is always available to assist you around the clock. When you contact us, you are getting a human on the other line, guaranteed. Additionally, we run all of our servers on enterprise grade equipment (with redundant power) \u2013 so you can be assured uptime and performance are at the forefront of our priorities when deploying infrastructure. We are overall here to make your hosting experience smooth, and if there is anything we can help you with, please don\u2019t hesitate to contact us!\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Here\u2019s the offers:&nbsp;</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>1GB OpenVZ VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>1 vCPU</li><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>15GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/OpenVZ</li><li>$12/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=96\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>1GB KVM VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>1 vCPU</li><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>10GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/KVM</li><li>Docker Supported</li><li>$15/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=97\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>2GB OpenVZ VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>2 vCPU\u2019s</li><li>2048MB RAM</li><li>40GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/OpenVZ</li><li>$18/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=92\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>2GB KVM VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>2 vCPU\u2019s</li><li>2048MB RAM</li><li>25GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/KVM</li><li>Docker Supported</li><li>$30/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=93\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>4GB OpenVZ VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>4 vCPU\u2019s</li><li>4096MB RAM</li><li>50GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/OpenVZ</li><li>$29/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=94\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>4GB KVM VPS (SSD)</b></p><ul><li>4 vCPU\u2019s</li><li>4096MB RAM</li><li>35GB SSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps Network</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>Full Root Access</li><li>SolusVM/KVM</li><li>Docker Supported</li><li>$45/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.snowvps.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=95\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-18377\"></span></p><div><strong>NETWORK INFO:</strong></div><p>SnowVPS\u2019 datacenter is located within the DuPont Fabros CH1 facility in Elk Grove Village, IL (just directly outside of Chicago).</p><p>The network blend consists of GTT and SCNET, please find a test IP &amp; file below:</p><p>Test IPv4: 66.225.198.198<br>\nTest file:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://66.225.198.198/1000MB.test\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">http://66.225.198.198/1000MB.test</a></p><hr><p><b>Host Node Specifications:</b></p><p>OpenVZ Host Node Specifications:<br>\n\u2013 Intel Xeon E3 CPU<br>\n\u2013 32GB DDR3 ECC RAM<br>\n\u2013 4x 1TB Samsung 860 PRO Series SSD<br>\n\u2013 LSI Hardware RAID-10 with LSI 9271<br>\n\u2013 Dual/Redundant Power Supply<br>\n\u2013 1Gbps Network Uplink</p><p>KVM Host Node Specifications:<br>\n\u2013 Dual Intel Xeon E5-2620v2<br>\n\u2013 128GB DDR3 ECC RAM<br>\n\u2013 8x 1TB Samsung 860 PRO Series SSD<br>\n\u2013 LSI Hardware RAID-10 with LSI 9271<br>\n\u2013 Dual/Redundant Power Supply<br>\n\u2013 1Gbps Network Uplink</p><p>Please let us know if you have any questions/comments and enjoy!</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fsnowvps-12-year-1gb-vz-ssd-vps-45-year-4gb-kvm-ssd-vps-and-more-in-chicago-il%2F&amp;t=SnowVPS%20-%20%2412%2Fyear%201GB%20VZ%20SSD%20VPS%2C%20%2445%2Fyear%204GB%20KVM%20SSD%20VPS%20and%20more%20in%20Chicago%2C%20IL%21\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share o